Package digilib.util

Class ImageSize

  • java.lang.Object
    • digilib.util.ImageSize
  • public class ImageSize
extends Object
    Class for image size (width, height). A width or height of 0 is treated as a 'wildcard' that matches any size.
    Author:
    casties
